<tr>
<th scope="col" class="org-left">Interface</th>
<th scope="col" class="org-left">Method(s)</th>
<th scope="col" class="org-left">Description</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="org-left"><code>IComparer</code></td>
<td class="org-left"><code>Compare(first, second)</code></td>
<td class="org-left">This defines a comparison method that a secondary type implements to order or sort instances of a primary type.</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left"><code>IComparable</code></td>
<td class="org-left"><code>CompareTo(other)</code></td>
<td class="org-left">This defines a comparison method that a type implements to order or sort its instances.</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td class="org-left"><code>IEnumerator</code></td>
